
DESCRIPTION
============

A simple shell implementation with following functions: 

  -- Execute the command inputed by user properly.

  -- Redirection.

  -- Pipe.

  -- Run in the background, with command nohup.

  -- History commands look up with up and down keys.

  -- Auto completion (Tab)

  -- Simple scripts: 

	1.  if [ number ]; then command; fi

    2.	while [ number ]; do command; done


BUILD AND RUN
=============
  You need the library of "readline".
  
  $ make
  $ ./jysh

